```plantuml
@startuml OpenIPC_motors

actor User as user
participant "Camera Application" as app
participant "Motors Daemon" as daemon
participant "Driver Wrapper" as wrapper
participant "Hardware Interface" as hardware

user -> app : Request motor control
app -> daemon : Send motor command
daemon -> wrapper : Select appropriate driver
wrapper -> hardware : Send hardware-specific command

note over hardware : Controls motor movement

hardware -> wrapper : Confirm execution
wrapper -> daemon : Acknowledge command
daemon -> app : Send confirmation to application
app -> user : Notify user of success

@enduml
```